Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.01,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,青リンゴ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:10.93,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱えてる胸の奥
